+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-only
+/*
+ * vDPA bus.
+ *
+ * Copyright (c) 2020, Red Hat. All rights reserved.
+ *     Author: Jason Wang <jasowang@redhat.com>
+ *
